data.title: The Cast of "Mean Girls" Finds Out Which Characters They Really Are
data.meta_description: Get in loser! To celebrate the release of “Mean Girls” we had the cast — Angourie Rice, Reneé Rapp, Auli’i Cravalho, Christopher Briney, Jaquel Spivey, Bebe Wood, and Avantika — take a quiz to find out which characters they actually are. Is Reneé really like Regina? Or does she have a little bit of Cady in her? Which original “Mean Girls” actor would they love to star in a movie with? Watch it all now and then take the quiz yourself to see who you are, too. #MeanGirls #ReneeRapp
